---
title: Creamy Dreamy Linguine with Mushrooms and Tarragon
description: Mushrooms in a creamy sauce never fails to hit the spot when you’re looking for pure comfort food. In this recipe, we’re incorporating those classic flavors into a tangle of al dente linguine pasta. Garlic, lemon, and anise-scented tarragon add uplifting accents and give the dish a deeply savory dimension.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-fettucine-with-mushrooms-f68c873c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-fettucine-with-mushrooms-5c077044.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
